  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a diagnostic evaluation comparing the performance of real-time PCR performed at a&#xD;
      national reference laboratory and a LAMP assay performed at a regional hospital for the&#xD;
      diagnosis of yaws&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
